  <entry>
    <title>字符与字符串</title>
    <link href="http://na-wen.github.io/2022/05/08/%E5%AD%97%E7%AC%A6%E4%B8%8E%E5%AD%97%E7%AC%A6%E4%B8%B2/"/>
    <id>http://na-wen.github.io/2022/05/08/%E5%AD%97%E7%AC%A6%E4%B8%8E%E5%AD%97%E7%AC%A6%E4%B8%B2/</id>
    <published>2022-05-08T04:41:58.000Z</published>
    <updated>2022-05-08T04:44:45.112Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>[TOC]</p><p>&lt;<span id="more"></span>&gt;</p><h2 id="字符系列类型"><a href="#字符系列类型" class="headerlink" title="字符系列类型"></a>字符系列类型</h2><p>char： 1 个字节 窄字符</p><p>wchar_t： 宽字符</p><p>char16_t   char32_t</p><p>不同的前缀对应着不同的类型：分别为  无前缀，L,u，U</p><h3 id="字符串字面常量"><a href="#字符串字面常量" class="headerlink" title="字符串字面常量"></a>字符串字面常量</h3><p>前缀部分+核心部分（类似字符）</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;string&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">u8&quot;string&quot;</span>      <span class="comment">//string :char UTF 8</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">L&quot;string&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">u&quot;string&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">U&quot;string&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>其中  wchar_t  对应的标准输入输出流为： wcin  wcout</p><p>每个字符集的组成，需要字符编码，需要具体字符；间有着映射关系</p><h3 id="汉字的输入输出"><a href="#汉字的输入输出" class="headerlink" title="汉字的输入输出"></a>汉字的输入输出</h3><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">locale basic_ios :: <span class="built_in">imbue</span>(<span class="type">const</span> locale&amp;_Loc);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//_Loc  本地系统局域设置</span></span><br><span class="line">locale ::<span class="built_in">locale</span> (<span class="type">const</span> <span class="type">char</span> *std_name);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//locale 类的构造函数  根据字符串的类型创建局域设置</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//使用</span></span><br><span class="line">wcout.<span class="built_in">imbue</span>(<span class="built_in">locale</span>(<span class="string">&quot;chs&quot;</span>));</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>是只能用wchar_t 才能完成汉字的输出吗？不是 和char最大的区别就在于单个的大小不同</p><h2 id="字符数组形式的字符串"><a href="#字符数组形式的字符串" class="headerlink" title="字符数组形式的字符串"></a>字符数组形式的字符串</h2><p>将多字节字符串转换为宽字符字符串的函数：</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">int</span> <span class="title">MultiByteToWideChar</span><span class="params">(UINT CodePage, DWORD dwFlags, LPCSTR lpMultiByteStr, <span class="type">int</span> cbMultiByte, LPWSTR lpWideCharStr, <span class="type">int</span> cchWideChar)</span></span>;</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//codepage  CP_ACP   CP_UTF8</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//dwFlags   指定一下字符串转换的方式</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//lpMultiByteStr  待转换的字符串  </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//cbMultiByte    待转换的字符个数   若为-1，表示要求待转换的字符串必须以0结尾</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//lpWideCharStr   转换后接收的内存空间</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//cchWideChar   转换后接受的内存空间大小</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//具体使用</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">char</span> pc[]=<span class="string">&quot;我想睡觉&quot;</span>；</span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">wchar_t</span>  pcw[<span class="number">100</span>];</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">MultiByteToWideChar</span>(CP_ACP,<span class="number">0</span>,pc,<span class="number">-1</span>,pcw,<span class="number">100</span>);</span><br><span class="line">wcout.<span class="built_in">imbue</span>(<span class="built_in">locale</span>(<span class="string">&quot;chs&quot;</span>));</span><br><span class="line">wcout&lt;&lt;pcw&lt;&lt;endl;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">size_t</span> <span class="title">mbstowcs</span><span class="params">(<span class="type">wchar_t</span> *wcstr, <span class="type">const</span> <span class="type">char</span> *mbstr, <span class="type">size_t</span> count)</span></span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//也可以进行转换  但是不安全 </span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">errno_t</span> <span class="title">mbstowcs_s</span><span class="params">(<span class="type">size_t</span> *pReturnValue, <span class="type">wchar_t</span> *wcstr, <span class="type">size_t</span> sizeInWords, <span class="type">const</span> <span class="type">char</span> *mbstr, <span class="type">size_t</span> count)</span></span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//这个VC平台支持</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">char</span> *<span class="title">setlocale</span><span class="params">(<span class="type">int</span> category, <span class="type">const</span> <span class="type">char</span> *locale)</span></span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>将宽字节字符串转换为多字节字符串</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">errno_t</span> <span class="title">wcstombs_s</span><span class="params">(<span class="type">size_t</span> *pReturnValue, <span class="type">char</span> *mbstr, <span class="type">size_t</span> sizeInBytes, <span class="type">const</span> <span class="type">wchar_t</span> *wcstr, <span class="type">size_t</span> count)</span></span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="字符串类"><a href="#字符串类" class="headerlink" title="字符串类"></a>字符串类</h3><p>string   wstring  u16string u32string </p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cout &lt;&lt; sh &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;: string\n&quot;</span> &lt;&lt; s8 &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;: string UTF-8\n&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// cout &lt;&lt; sw &lt;&lt; &quot;: wstring\n&quot;;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// cout &lt;&lt; s6 &lt;&lt; &quot;: u16string\n&quot; &lt;&lt; s2 &lt;&lt; &quot;: u32string\n&quot;;</span></span><br><span class="line">    wcout.<span class="built_in">imbue</span>(<span class="built_in">locale</span>(<span class="string">&quot;chs&quot;</span>));</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// wcout &lt;&lt; sh &lt;&lt; &quot;: string\n&quot; &lt;&lt; s8 &lt;&lt; &quot;: string UTF-8\n&quot;;</span></span><br><span class="line">    wcout &lt;&lt; sw &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;: wstring\n&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// wcout &lt;&lt; s6 &lt;&lt; &quot;: u16string\n&quot; &lt;&lt; s2 &lt;&lt; &quot;: u32string\n&quot;;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//惊闻此处去掉注释编译会不通过 但自己跑了去掉注释没有什么问题...</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="构造函数"><a href="#构造函数" class="headerlink" title="构造函数"></a>构造函数</h4><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function">string <span class="title">s</span><span class="params">(<span class="string">&quot;12345678&quot;</span>)</span></span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function">string <span class="title">b</span><span class="params">(s,<span class="number">2</span>,<span class="number">3</span>)</span></span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//345</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function">string <span class="title">c</span><span class="params">(s,<span class="number">0</span>,<span class="number">7</span>)</span></span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//1234567</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">string</span> (<span class="number">4</span>,<span class="string">&#x27;a&#x27;</span>);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//aaaa</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="迭代器"><a href="#迭代器" class="headerlink" title="迭代器"></a>迭代器</h4><h4 id="容量与长度"><a href="#容量与长度" class="headerlink" title="容量与长度"></a>容量与长度</h4><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">s.<span class="built_in">capacity</span>();</span><br><span class="line">s.<span class="built_in">length</span>();</span><br><span class="line">s.<span class="built_in">size</span>();</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>其他的函数操作与vector类似</p><h4 id="字符串转换为字符数组的形式"><a href="#字符串转换为字符数组的形式" class="headerlink" title="字符串转换为字符数组的形式"></a>字符串转换为字符数组的形式</h4><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">const</span> charT* <span class="title">c_str</span><span class="params">()</span></span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">const</span> charT * <span class="title">data</span><span class="params">()</span></span>;</span><br><span class="line">s.<span class="built_in">data</span>();</span><br><span class="line">s.<span class="built_in">c_str</span>();</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="成员"><a href="#成员" class="headerlink" title="成员"></a>成员</h4><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">s.<span class="built_in">at</span>(<span class="number">1</span>);</span><br><span class="line">s[<span class="number">1</span>];</span><br><span class="line">s.<span class="built_in">front</span>();</span><br><span class="line">s.<span class="built_in">back</span>();</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>有待学习的问题： 编码方式 </p>]]></content>
    
    
